schools.name: Rim Of The World Senior High School

data.description: This was once one of the nicest homes in the San Moritz area of Lake Gregory. It has fallen into disrepair, and needs some fixing up to bring back its charm. It is a steal at this price, and is being sold in its current "as is" "as disclosed" condition. This charming home sits on two lots with wonderful mountain views and a slight peek of Lake Gregory from the vacant lot to the left of the home that is included in the listing price. The main level features a bedroom and a full bath, plus a foyer as you walk in the front door to the kitchen and dining area. The living room has two story beamed ceilings and a wood burning stove. There is a deck off the living room that sustained some damage from the heavy snow this past winter. The deck does need to be repaired or replaced. The upper level features an open loft that overlooks the living room. The lower level has another bedroom and bathroom, plus a very large laundry room. The home is located close to Lake Gregory, dining, bowling, the post office and the library. Detached from the home is a large covered carport with a workshop at the end of it. There's room for 3 cars in the driveway too. Bring your imagination and tool bag and bring this home back to it's original charm.    The property consists of 2 lots, Lots 34 and 35 Tract 3685. They are both listed under the same APN.
